    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm not asking for help or a lecture. I'm just... I'm trying to express the weight of this grief. It's a story, a feeling. It feels so poetic, like the only way a heart this broken could ever find peace is to simply stop beating, to vanish like mist in the morning. Don't you see the tragedy in that? The beauty of a life ending when its purpose has been taken away?",
